<div type="bibliography">
<p>No visual documentation seems to have been published for the present inscription, for which nearly identical readings have been published. Not having identified the slab bearing this inscription, we are unable to verify the published readings. The text we propose here is an attempt to interpret and normalize the published readings.</p>
